---
title: Seared Chicken & Roasted Spud Burger with Red Wine Jus & Cabbage Slaw
description: Gather around the table to get a bite of this chicken burger. Make it an occasion and invite some friends to join the team spirit, everyone will love the roasted spud slices! We’re sure you’ll be this burger’s biggest fan.
